1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 1=

3
00:01:24,599 --> 00:01:25,879
So eager?

4
00:01:25,959 --> 00:01:26,719
Do you like it?

5
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:31,040
Yes.

6
00:01:31,079 --> 00:01:32,439
Is the promotion list out?

7
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:33,519
What?

8
00:01:34,719 --> 00:01:36,200
You still want a promotion?

9
00:01:36,439 --> 00:01:38,519
At work, I help
the boss convince clients.

10
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,959
In private, I "manage" his wife.

11
00:01:41,079 --> 00:01:42,359
I'm doing two men's work.

12
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,359
GM is the least I deserve.

13
00:01:44,799 --> 00:01:46,120
That drug is strong.

14
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:50,200
It will make her burn with desire.

15
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:53,040
I'll make you burn with desire first.

16
00:02:04,384 --> 00:02:10,240
♪Love can grow from a small place♪

17
00:02:12,064 --> 00:02:14,272
♪A taste of pleasure♪

18
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:19,392
♪Of trust and time together♪

19
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:21,599
Want some fun?

20
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,400
I don't want to take advantage.

21
00:02:24,064 --> 00:02:26,624
♪Heartfelt cheering♪

22
00:02:28,039 --> 00:02:28,960
I want.

23
00:02:29,439 --> 00:02:30,624
You said it.

24
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:33,039
Don't regret it later.

25
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:39,136
♪Hand in hand♪

26
00:02:39,136 --> 00:02:43,520
♪All these times we spent♪

27
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,000
Ji Xuan, long time no see.

28
00:02:45,039 --> 00:02:46,479
What did you just call me?

29
00:02:47,744 --> 00:02:50,880
♪Heart to heart♪

30
00:02:51,264 --> 00:02:53,824
♪Hand in hand♪

31
00:02:53,824 --> 00:02:58,464
♪All these times we spent♪

32
00:02:58,464 --> 00:03:01,920
♪They are ours♪

33
00:03:02,016 --> 00:03:04,192
♪They are ours♪

34
00:03:04,256 --> 00:03:06,880
♪Hand in hand♪

35
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,400
The man from last night took me home?

36
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,599
Why can't I remember
what he looked like?

37
00:03:52,639 --> 00:03:53,319
Forget it.

38
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:56,080
Today is the day I first met Mr. Song.

39
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:59,520
I can't let anything affect me.

40
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,728
(Zhang Bin)

41
00:04:39,279 --> 00:04:39,800
Hello?

42
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,959
Miss Ji, bad news, something's happened.

43
00:05:07,839 --> 00:05:09,959
Ji Xuan, what are you playing at?

44
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:13,360
I just introduced you
to all our major partners yesterday.

45
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:16,839
This morning, everyone
received your scandalous photos.

46
00:05:18,079 --> 00:05:19,759
You've completely humiliated me.

47
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:22,000
Mr. Li, I was framed.

48
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:24,319
Give me two days.
I'll give you an explanation.

49
00:05:24,319 --> 00:05:25,519
You still don't get it.

50
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:28,000
People won't care about the truth.

51
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:29,759
The public decides what's real.

52
00:05:30,079 --> 00:05:32,079
We spent a lot to poach you

53
00:05:32,199 --> 00:05:34,319
to generate profit for the company,

54
00:05:34,319 --> 00:05:36,360
not to tarnish the company's reputation.

55
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:38,920
And I even let you handle
the Song Group project.

56
00:05:43,279 --> 00:05:44,560
You're not suited to work here.

57
00:05:46,879 --> 00:05:49,199
You're just afraid the deal
with Mr. Song will fail.

58
00:05:49,319 --> 00:05:50,560
I'll explain to him myself.

59
00:06:02,959 --> 00:06:03,759
Mr. Song.

60
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:04,759
Mr. Song.

61
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,480
Mr. Song is quite impressive.

62
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,319
Mr. Song.

63
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,399
Look at you, coming personally.

64
00:06:18,759 --> 00:06:20,319
I was just about to go out to meet you.

65
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:27,319
Here, Mr. Song, have some tea.

66
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:32,480
This is Miss Ji,
the one involved in the scandal?

67
00:06:33,519 --> 00:06:35,560
- Mr. Song, she is now...
- Mr. Song.

68
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:36,800
Don't misunderstand.

69
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:39,879
The person with me
last night was my boyfriend.

70
00:06:41,759 --> 00:06:45,680
So it was your boyfriend last night.

71
00:06:49,199 --> 00:06:52,439
You and your boyfriend
like to spice things up?

72
00:06:54,519 --> 00:06:55,680
Mr. Song, don't worry.

73
00:06:56,279 --> 00:06:58,680
My personal life won't affect my work.

74
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,120
Let's talk business.

75
00:07:00,352 --> 00:07:00,920
Mr. Li.

76
00:07:01,408 --> 00:07:02,120
Mr. Song.

77
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,839
Have Miss Ji discuss
any matters with me.

78
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:04,800
You may go.

79
00:07:05,024 --> 00:07:06,800
Alright then, you two talk.

80
00:07:07,456 --> 00:07:08,079
Leaving.

81
00:07:10,959 --> 00:07:14,240
You look quite special in men's clothes.

82
00:07:15,759 --> 00:07:17,000
This isn't men's clothing.

83
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:20,079
It's an oversized,
new style of women's wear.

84
00:07:24,439 --> 00:07:27,079
(The Coal Factory Project)
Mr. Song, this is the proposal I made.

85
00:07:27,079 --> 00:07:28,920
The way you handle public opinion

86
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:31,199
is far more interesting than this.

87
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,570
You hold a high position
and great power.

88
00:07:36,570 --> 00:07:37,800
I won't deceive you.

89
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:40,319
But compared to my private life,

90
00:07:40,519 --> 00:07:41,879
surely what you care more about

91
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:44,519
is who can present a satisfying plan.

92
00:07:45,319 --> 00:07:47,040
(Seems she really doesn't recognize me.)

93
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:48,680
(Interesting.)

94
00:07:49,759 --> 00:07:53,560
Miss Ji, I can't see
the data on this clearly.

95
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:58,319
Mr. Song, this is an ultra-HD screen.

96
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,399
The blue light screen hurts my eyes.

97
00:08:01,079 --> 00:08:03,360
Please give me a hard copy.

98
00:08:13,639 --> 00:08:14,759
So sorry, Mr. Song.

99
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:18,920
Mr. Song, I'm sorry.

100
00:08:30,639 --> 00:08:32,080
You're quite wild.

101
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:39,600
Mr. Song, I'll buy you a new suit.

102
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,799
No need, I have another set in my car.

103
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,424
I need to compensate you.

104
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,000
Okay.

105
00:09:01,399 --> 00:09:02,679
No time like the present.

106
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:04,919
How about today?

107
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:06,919
(Later, I came to realize)

108
00:09:07,399 --> 00:09:11,120
(I was caught in his game
from the very beginning.)

109
00:09:11,279 --> 00:09:12,120
Welcome.

110
00:09:26,799 --> 00:09:27,480
Mr. Song.

111
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,960
This shop doesn't seem
to sell men's clothes.

112
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,759
You said you'd buy me clothes.

113
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:36,039
So what we buy
should be up to me, right?

114
00:09:36,399 --> 00:09:37,120
Alright.

115
00:09:37,919 --> 00:09:40,440
I didn't expect you
to have this kind of hobby.

116
00:09:40,448 --> 00:09:41,080
Pick one.

117
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:42,720
Which one do you like?

118
00:09:43,639 --> 00:09:44,639
I'll take that one.

119
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,639
This one is quite beautiful.

120
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:55,159
Could you get this for me?

121
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,559
Your measurements?

122
00:09:56,559 --> 00:09:58,000
I'll recommend the right size.

123
00:09:58,279 --> 00:09:58,840
Measurements.

124
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,080
81.

125
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,240
60.

126
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:02,440
89.

127
00:10:03,279 --> 00:10:04,080
81.

128
00:10:12,879 --> 00:10:13,840
I meant yours.

129
00:10:13,879 --> 00:10:14,679
Yours.

130
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,600
How do you know?

131
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:22,720
Because my girlfriend's figure
is identical to yours.

132
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,559
Sir, this is the dress you wanted.

133
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:34,159
This dress suits you better.

134
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,159
It's yours.

135
00:10:37,039 --> 00:10:38,240
I can't accept this.

136
00:10:38,399 --> 00:10:40,960
Besides, I promised
to compensate you with clothes.

137
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,799
Then it should be

138
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:44,720
me compensating you.

139
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:57,159
Xuan.

140
00:10:58,080 --> 00:11:00,279
Don't forget the Rongsheng ball tonight.

141
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:01,879
I'll be there.

142
00:11:22,848 --> 00:11:24,640
♪In the vast sea of stars♪

143
00:11:24,800 --> 00:11:26,680
♪Flickering neon lights♪

144
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:30,208
♪Longing spreads
throughout the universe♪

145
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:32,992
♪Every star is♪

146
