♪You are the painful greeting
in my despair♪

154
00:12:01,568 --> 00:12:04,480
♪Can't find a cure♪

155
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:08,992
♪To love you after we've parted♪

156
00:12:09,184 --> 00:12:13,216
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

157
